Definition: the imparting of news or promises etc.
Example: he gave us the news and made a great show of the giving; giving his word of honor seemed to come too easily
Synonyms: verb, possession, give, communication, conveyance, the, imparting, of, news, or, promises, etc, he, gave, us, and, made, a, great, show, his, word, honor, seemed, to, come, too, easily
Category: noun.communication
